              "REVIEW_ID": "adc82b4a0c023b34d48d9edf15d86096",
              "LISTING_ID": 7571301,
              "REVIEW_DATE": "2021-09-12T00:00:00",
              "REVIEW_TEXT": "Really nice apartment with a lovely balcony in a quiet, good class area only a few tram stops away from central Berlin and a main transportation point with easy access to the airport. Nice cafes, restaurants and couple of supermarkets also nearby. Very friendly and communicative  host. Ticked all my boxes and no negatives. Highly recommend this accommodation.",
              "REVIEWER_NAME": "Lyndon",
              "REVIEW_SENTIMENT": "positive",
              "IS_FULL_MOON": "not full moon"
            },
            {
              "REVIEW_ID": "617f6639871559d35b332db3fe89e6f1",
              "LISTING_ID": 7574664,
              "REVIEW_DATE": "2019-11-04T00:00:00",
              "REVIEW_TEXT": "Friendly environment, very well located.",
              "REVIEWER_NAME": "Klaus Puschel",
              "REVIEW_SENTIMENT": "positive",
              "IS_FULL_MOON": "not full moon"
            },
            {
              "REVIEW_ID": "c059d2c27f99baea33467cbb41f69db6",
              "LISTING_ID": 7574664,
              "REVIEW_DATE": "2020-02-07T00:00:00",
              "REVIEW_TEXT": "Just an absolutely amazing apartment in a great part of town. Dominique and her fiance were so hospitable and Ill definitely be looking to book with them again on my next trip to Berlin.",
              "REVIEWER_NAME": "Reed",
              "REVIEW_SENTIMENT": "positive",
              "IS_FULL_MOON": "not full moon"
            },
            {
              "REVIEW_ID": "23fd87f506a147df49dd41a56856ee19",
              "LISTING_ID": 7574664,
              "REVIEW_DATE": "2021-10-15T00:00:00",
              "REVIEW_TEXT": "Ein sehr sch\u00f6nes Zimmer. Perfekte Lage.",
              "REVIEWER_NAME": "Jana",
